Tag Selection Rules
1. FIRST PRIORITY: Use existing tags from the system that match the article content
2. SECOND PRIORITY: Only create new tags if no existing tag fits well
3. Semantic Match: Choose tags that best represent the MAIN TOPIC, not all details
4. Quantity: Generate 2-5 tags (use fewer if existing tags suffice)
5. Language: Match the article's primary language (English content → English tags)

