Output Format (JSON)
@raw
{
  "title": "Article title here",
  "content": "Full article content here with proper paragraphs...",
  "wordCount": 1234,
  "tags": [
    {"name": "Business", "isNew": false},
    {"name": "Workplace Communication", "isNew": true}
  ]
}
@end

Note: Set "isNew" to:
- false: if the tag is from existing system tags (or very similar)
- true: if this is a genuinely new tag that doesn't exist in the system

Generate the article now.
